    <text type="letter"> 
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_zs.00408.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>Medical Superintendent's</name>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>Office</name>
                    <name type="place">INSANE ASYLUM</name>
                    <name type="place">LONDON ONTARIO<ptr target="loc.08175_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1891-10-13"><handShift rend="manuscript"/>13 Oct. <handShift
                            rend="printed"/>18<handShift rend="manuscript"/>91</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>I have your letter of 10<hi rend="underline">th</hi><ptr target="loc.08175_n2"/> I
                fear you are not having a good time and I guess this change in the weather from hot
                to almost cold will not be favorable to you&#8212;I wish you would ask Longaker<ptr
                    target="loc.08039_n2"/> if he does not think a steam bath (with alcohol lamp)
                would be good for you&#8212;say about once&#8212;or even twice a week? <hi
                    rend="underline">Here</hi> all goes well&#8212;bright, crisp weather and all in
                good health&#8212;pretty busy, but <hi rend="underline">that</hi> does no
                harm&#8212;Inspector<ptr target="loc.04984_n3"/> is to be here tomorrow or next day&#8212;I am about half
                through my annual report&#8212;I hear nothing from you or Horace<ptr target="n4267"
                /> about the new L. of G.<ptr target="loc.04811_n6"/>&#8212;What are you doing with
                it? Send me a line as often as possible&#8212;I cannot do much for you but I am here
                to do what I can</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>With best Love</salute>
                <signed>R M Bucke</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc_zs.00409.jpg" type="recto"/>
